* Persist Change\nHistory Long-Term
** Delta Log Limitations
***_ Default 30-day retention
***_ VACUUM removes older files
** Long-Term Patterns
***_ Write CDF to separate history table
***_ Append-only history archive
***_ Include metadata (source file, load time)
** History Table Design
***_ All original columns
***_ _change_type, _commit_timestamp
***_ Partition by date for efficiency
** Compliance
***_ Immutable history (no updates/deletes)
***_ Documented retention policies
@endmindmap
